# CPListImageRowItemCondensedElement.Shape

**Enumeration**

Types of shape used to draw a condensed row element.

## Declaration

```swift
enum Shape
```

## Enumeration Cases

- **CPListImageRowItemCondensedElement.Shape.circular**: The list item will render an element with a circular image.
- **CPListImageRowItemCondensedElement.Shape.roundedRectangle**: The list item will render an element with a rounded rectangle image.
